## GET /v1/test
The first description

### Example
#### Request
<details> 
  <summary>
Header
  </summary>

```
GET /v1/test HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer xyz
```
</details>

#### Response
<details>
  <summary>
Header
  </summary>

#### HTTP version and status code
```
HTTP/1.1 200
```

#### Header
```
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
```

</details>

<details>
  <summary>
Body
  </summary>

```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "name: "fisrt"
}
```

</details>
